Dependencies
--------------------------------------------------

* recent libnuma (I used 2.0.8, which I was compiling separately)
    the path to libnuma then needs to be specified in the Makefile, l.9

Compile
--------------------------------------------------

$ make pt_bench_pairs_ump

Execute
--------------------------------------------------

From the main directory:
$ scripts/pairwise.py

If you compiled your own libnuma:
$ LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/path/to/libnuma scripts/pairwise.py

This will generate output files /tmp/send and /tmp/receive

Problems
--------------------------------------------------

